data.title: USA Latitude and Longitude Map
data.text:
USA Latitude and Longitude Map is a clickable US map with clearly mentioned Latitude and Longitude. Latitude and Longitude refer to angles, measured in degrees (1 degree = 60 minutes of arc) that tell you the exact location of a country, city, etc. on a map. Just click any state in this US map and itâll take you to an enlarged Lat Long Map of that state showing state capital, county seats, state boundaries, and country boundaries with latitudes and longitudes plotted on it.
